## 1. Introduction
- Overview of NutriBuddy
- Problem statement: Personalized diet planning & meal analysis using AI

## 2. Objectives
- Analyze meals (calories, macros)
- Suggest high-protein recipes
- Respond to dietary queries via AI agent

## 3. Tools & Technologies Used
- IBM Watsonx Agent Lab (Granite Model)
- Google Search Tool
- NLP (Natural Language Processing)
- Python (optional logic)
- Gradio (UI - optional)

## 4. Sample Inputs & Expected Responses
### Example 1:
**Input:** "I had roti, dal and salad for lunch."  
**Output:** ~600 kcal, 30g protein, balanced meal

### Example 2:
**Input:** "Suggest a 150g protein vegetarian diet"  
**Output:** Full day meal plan with macros

## 5. IBM Watsonx Agent Integration
- Agent name: NutriBuddy_AI_Agent
- Model: Granite-3B (initially LLaMA-3)
- Tools: Google Search + [Custom Tool â€“ Future Plan]
